## Security Notes

All ported commits were reviewed for:
- Hardcoded credentials (none found after sanitization)
- Personal wallet addresses (sanitized in dashboard_config.json)
- Personal LAN IP addresses (sanitized in dashboard_config.json)
- Personal operational settings (port remaps, Werkzeug flag, Grafana
  exposure, difficulty config — all reverted to maintain compatibility)
- Supply chain risks (BTCS Dockerfile pinned to commit ff5c3c3d via
  targeted git fetch; BCH2 Dockerfile updated to v27.0.2 with correct
  release URL format)
